Notes: Game was tied at 8-8 with 16:12 remaining when SP went on 33-0 run over the
next eight minutes and 45 seconds to take 41-8 lead... SP led by as many as
56 points... SP tied a season high with 96 points which they reached both
times versus Superior... SP's 16th consecutive win over Superior.
